name: tools_release
description: Cut and publish a release — gate, bump every manifest, commit, tag, and push so CI builds the binaries. Use when the user asks to ship a specific MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH version.
kind: tool
tags: [release, publish, ci, cargo, tag]
use_when: [publish a version, cut a release, tag and publish, ship it]
